Description: Fragment of flattened handle from a Knidian pottery transport amphora. Clay near fine orange-brown with white inclusions; cream slip. Circular stamp at top of handle with Greek inscription.
Type series: KT1423 (Virginia Grace's unpublished K(nidian) T(ype) series)
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (JB.0273)
